snippet.textDisplay:
Coke Studio seems to lack quality people who can select better lyrics. We have brilliant writers in Urdu and Punjabi (both past and present) whose work can be appreciated through good music. Such bland and dreary compositions won't serve the purpose. 

Akhtar Usman, Irfan Sattar, Tahira Saraa, Umair Najmi, Ammar Iqbal aur kitne aise naam haiN jo bohat acha likh rahe haiN. Aur CS waale kya utha laate haiN. Afsos!
